high_descs: Turn to your left and head to the door across the room then turn right and face the white table
Pick up the egg that is sitting on the table.
Turn to your right and hang a right once you pass the table, then walk to the microwave
Open the microwave and place the egg inside then close the microwave and turn it on. Open the microwave and pick up the egg that is inside and then close the microwave
Turn right and talk to the fridge, then turn right and walk to the white table.
Place the egg on the table to the left of the potato.
anns.task_desc: Place a cooked egg on a table

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the door then turn right.
Pick up the egg to the left of the teapot.
Turn right and take a few steps so you're even with the red microwave on your right then turn right and walk to it.
Cook the egg in the microwave and then get it back out and close the door.
Go back to where you got the egg.
Put the egg to the left of the potato near the edge.
anns.task_desc: Put a microwaved egg on the table.

high_descs: Turn left and head to the table next to the door.
Pick up the egg on the table.
Turn around and bring the egg to the microwave on the right.
Heat the egg in the microwave.
Take the heated egg, turn around and go to the table on the left.
Put the heated egg on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated egg on the table.
